{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10287", "repo": "rails", "body": "@josevalim makes sense that Active Model should not know about `save` and friends.\r\n\r\nDo you have any suggestion in how to go about fixing this issue ?\r\n\r\nActive Model sets validation callbacks with condition `:save`. However Active Record only works with `:create` and `:update`.  \r\n\r\nOne solution could be that Active Model provides a hook for Active Record to override `:context` value before it is used in the condition . Not sure how complex it would be implementation wise.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237e0e5bd3543c151008f1c"}, "issue_id": 10287, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/16739210", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10287#issuecomment-16739210", "updated_at": "2013-04-21T18:36:54Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname", "login": "neerajdotname", "gravatar_id": "934f858e451cf9b771996b2940cd696b", "html_url": "https://github.com/neerajdotname", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/934f858e451cf9b771996b2940cd696b?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F985e9a46e10005356bbaf194249f6856.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 6399, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/neerajdotname/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-04-21T18:36:54Z", "id": 16739210, "owner": "rails"}
